sub_title: Human rights defender | gender equity&equality | CRSV&GBV | post-conflict peacebuilding | transformative gender justice
summary: Human rights defender with international NGO experience in researching and advocating in transitional justice responses to gender-based violations during conflict and humanitarian crises. Knowledgeable in conflict-related sexual violence and gender-based violence in the Western Balkans, Southeast Asia and Africa, while motivated to apply abilities and excel in policy, international peacebuilding, and conflict prevention.
